Contact#confirmation_email

<%= @greeting %>

Thank you for reaching out to Wrantle. We've received your <%= @contact.contact_type.humanize.downcase %> request.

Here's a summary of what you submitted:

Contact Details:
--------------
Name: <%= @contact.name %>
Email: <%= @contact.email %>
Phone: <%= @contact.phone %>

<% if @contact.contact_type == "schedule_chat" %>
Preferred Meeting Time:
--------------------
Date: <%= @contact.preferred_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
Time: <%= @contact.preferred_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %>

<% end %>
Your Message:
-----------
<%= @contact.message %>

<% if @contact.contact_type == "schedule_chat" %>
We'll review your preferred meeting time and confirm the schedule shortly.
<% elsif @contact.contact_type == "request_info" %>
We'll gather the information you need and get back to you soon.
<% else %>
We'll review your needs and provide a detailed assessment shortly.
<% end %>

Best regards,
The Wrantle Team

---
If you did not submit this request, please contact us immediately at support@wrantle.com
